<body lang=en-NL link="#0563C1" vlink="#96607D" style='tab-interval:36.0pt;
word-wrap:break-word'>

<div class=WordSection1>

<h1><span style='font-size:18.0pt'>Privacy Policy — Progress Fitness Tracker</span></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal><i><span style='font-size:10.0pt;color:#666666'>Last
updated: March 21, 2026</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>1. Who we are</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>Progress is a personal fitness tracking app developed by Pim
Croon. If you have questions about this policy, contact: pimcroondb@gmail.com</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>2. What data we collect</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>When you use Progress, we collect and store the following
data that you provide directly:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Account
data: email address and display name used to create your account</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Body
metrics: weight entries, body measurements, body fat percentage</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Fitness
activity: workout logs (exercises, sets, reps, weight), cardio activities</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Nutrition:
food entries and macro nutrients you log</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Health
goals: goal weight, target pace, height, phases and reference points</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Profile:
display name and optional profile picture (stored locally on your device only)</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>App
feedback: messages you submit via the in-app feedback form</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>We also request access to Apple Health (HealthKit) to read
and write:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Body
weight</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Body
fat percentage</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Heart
rate and HRV</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Sleep
data</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Steps
and respiratory rate</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Resting
heart rate</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>HealthKit data is only used to display your health trends
within the app. It is never shared with third parties or uploaded to our
servers. HealthKit data will not be used for advertising, data mining, or any
purpose other than health and fitness features within the app.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>3. How we store your data</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>Your account and fitness data is stored securely on Supabase
(supabase.com), a hosted database platform, on servers located in the European
Union (EU West — Ireland). Data is protected with row-level security — you can
only access your own data.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>Your profile picture is stored locally on your device only
and is never uploaded to our servers.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>Data is retained for as long as your account is active. When
you delete your account, all your data is permanently and immediately deleted
from our servers.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>4. Legal basis for processing (GDPR)</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>As a Dutch developer, this app is subject to the General
Data Protection Regulation (GDPR / AVG). We process your personal data on the
following legal grounds:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Consent:
you explicitly consent to data collection when creating an account and when
granting HealthKit access</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Contract
performance: processing is necessary to provide the app’s core functionality</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>5. What we do NOT do</h2>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>We
do not sell your data to anyone</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>We
do not share your data with advertisers</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>We
do not use your data for any purpose other than running the app for you</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>We
do not collect data in the background when the app is closed</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>We
do not use HealthKit data for advertising, data mining, or third-party
analytics</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>6. Third-party services</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>The app optionally integrates with:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Strava
— if you connect your Strava account, we fetch your activity data from Strava’s
API. This requires you to authorize the connection explicitly. You can
disconnect at any time in Settings.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Open
Food Facts — when you scan a barcode in the Nutrition module, a request is sent
to the Open Food Facts public API to look up food data. No personal data is
sent.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>7. Your rights</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Right
to access: request a copy of your data by emailing [your email here]</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Right
to deletion: delete your account at any time from the Profile screen — this
permanently deletes all your data</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Right
to portability: request your data in a portable format by emailing [your email
here]</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Right
to object: disconnect Strava or revoke HealthKit access at any time in Settings</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>•<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><![endif]>Right
to lodge a complaint: you may file a complaint with the Dutch Data Protection
Authority (Autoriteit Persoonsgegevens) at autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>8. Children</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>This app is not directed at children under 13 and we do not
knowingly collect data from children under 13. If you believe a child has
provided personal data, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>If we make significant changes, we will update the date at
the top of this policy and notify users via the app where required. Continued
use of the app after changes means you accept the updated policy.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p class=MsoNormal>Pim Croon — pimcroondb@gmail.com</p>

</div>

</body>

</html>
